author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Moscow Exchange FY 2017 Net Profit RUB 20.26 Bln, Down 19.6% YR/YR
text:
March 2 (Reuters) - Moscow Exchange:
* Q4 REVENUE RUB 9.59 BILLION, DOWN 6.3% VERSUS YEAR AGO * FY 2017 NET PROFIT OF RUB 20.26‍​ BILLION, DOWN 19.6% VERSUS YEAR AGO
* Q4 NET PROFIT RUB 4.81 BILLION, DOWN 12.6% VERSUS YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 REVENUE RUB 38.53​ BILLION, DOWN 11.5% VERSUS YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 FEE AND COMMISSION INCOME RUB 21.2 BILLION, UP 7.1% VERSUS YEAR AGO Source text - bit.ly/2CSlnef
